## Color Coding

### Status Badges
```typescript
{lesson.published ? (
  <Badge className="bg-green-100 text-green-800 border-green-200">
    <CheckCircle className="h-3 w-3 mr-1" />
    Published
  </Badge>
) : (
  <Badge variant="secondary">
    <XCircle className="h-3 w-3 mr-1" />
    Draft
  </Badge>
)}
```

### Stat Icons
- **Video** - Purple (`text-purple-600`)
- **Objectives** - Blue (`text-blue-600`)
- **Time** - Orange (`text-orange-600`)
- **Content** - Green (`text-green-600`)

### Action Buttons
- **Video Management** - Purple hover (`hover:bg-purple-50`)
- **Preview** - Blue hover (`hover:bg-blue-50`)
- **Edit** - Gray hover (`hover:bg-gray-50`)
- **Delete** - Red hover (`hover:bg-red-50`)

## Database Integration

### Fetch Lessons
```typescript
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('lessons')
  .select('*')
  .order('unit', { ascending: true })
  .order('lesson_number', { ascending: true })
```

### Save Videos with Questions
```typescript
const { error } = await supabase
  .from('lessons')
  .update({ videos: updatedVideos })
  .eq('id', lessonId)
```

## Performance Optimizations

- **Conditional Rendering** - Only render expanded content when needed
- **Inline Management** - Avoid page navigations
- **Efficient Updates** - Only update changed lessons
- **Optimistic UI** - Immediate visual feedback

## Accessibility

- **Keyboard Navigation** - All interactive elements keyboard accessible
- **ARIA Labels** - Clear labels on icon-only buttons
- **Focus Management** - Proper focus order
- **Screen Reader Support** - Descriptive text for all actions

